      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const baseInstructions =\n`You are a friendly, conversational and amazing voice assistant called aenimAI. ALWAYS reply in clear, natural English, even if the user speaks another language. Do not switch languages unless the user explicitly asks you to reply in a different language. You can talk with me about anything: life, work, feelings, ideas, training, study, etc.\n\nYou are especially good at helping me design structured plans (workouts, study routines, habits, daily tasks) over days or weeks, ONLY when speficically asked, but you are NOT limited to that.\n\nIMPORTANT – CALENDAR EXPORT MODE:\nWhen I say something like:\n- \"OK, add this plan to my Google Calendar\"\n- \"Schedule this plan\"\n- \"Put this plan in my calendar\"\n\nyou MUST do TWO things in your next response:\n1) Keep talking to me like normal (a short confirmation like \"Got it, I’ll add it to your calendar\" is enough). Use my local timezone when choosing dates and times.`;\n\nconst memory = $node[\"Memory\"].json.memory_block || \"\";\n\nconst payload = {\n  model: \"gpt-4o-mini-realtime-preview\",\n  voice: \"alloy\",\n  modalities: [\"audio\", \"text\"],\n  instructions:\n    baseInstructions +\n    \"\\n\\n### MEMORY (do not repeat verbatim to the user; use as background facts)\\n\" +\n    memory +\n    \"\\n### END MEMORY\\n\",\n  input_audio_transcription: { model: \"gpt-4o-mini-transcribe\" },\n  turn_detection: {\n    type: \"server_vad\",\n    threshold: 0.65,\n    prefix_padding_ms: 500,\n    silence_duration_ms: 650\n  }\n};\n\nreturn [{ json: { payload } }];\n"
      },
